  "_flat_structure_note": "This registry is domain-agnostic. The domain gate in assess_test_code_recognition() ensures codes are only looked up for domains in _TEST_CODE_DICTIONARY_DOMAINS. No two domains in the current corpus use the same code with conflicting semantics.",
